Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:15.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,旅の者だが　この雨で難儀している
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一晩軒を借りられんだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃご苦労だな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あがって休んでいくといい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:27.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,へえ　蟲師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:33.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あ　何か具合の悪いところや奇妙なことでもあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:36.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,役に立てるかもしれんが　どうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:41.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　うちはみんな丈夫なのが取り柄だな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:43.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,困ったことと言や　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:47.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,働けど働けど楽にはならんということぐらいか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:49.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:54.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,旅をしてるなら　他所の土地の話を聞かせてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう長いことこの里から出てないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:03.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,世話になったな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:08.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何の　いろいろ変わった話が聞けて面白かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺ら　平凡に暮らしてきたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:16.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何ごともないのが一番いいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それじゃ　達者で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　あんたもな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すっかり遅くなっちまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く帰らねぇと　あいつが心配する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:50.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,花の…匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まただ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:59.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また何か大事なことを忘れてるような…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな洞があったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰かが掘ったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:17.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,花の匂い　この中からだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　どこかに出られるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この方向なら　里への近道かもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,花の匂いで噎せ返るようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:49.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体なんだったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:53.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何を忘れてしまってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう　確か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:06.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,遠い　遠い昔のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,カオル
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに　母様
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お茶が入ったわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ならんならん　いい加減にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:32.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,年々評判は落ちるばかりじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:36.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,賃上げしろと言うなら　もっとましな酒作ってみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ですが　今の賃料では…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,口答えするな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あなたは気にしなくていいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なあ　おい　これ取れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだよ　あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やってません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,嘘をつくな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,カオルが見たと言ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　謝れんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　とっとと出て行け
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうなってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,全部　抜かれてるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体誰がこんなこと…
