Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:10.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうだ 何かを忘れてる気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:18.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか　あんたは「廻陋」に囚われちまったのかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:25.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,花のような匂いを出し　虫や獣を誘い込む
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,漆黒の筒状の蟲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:35.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　誘い込んだ獲物の時間を円環状に歪めると言われている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:43.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だとすれば　そいつは同じ時間を繰り返し生かされることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,繰り返し…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰にも確かめる術はない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:54.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,が　もし　そうだとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたはもう同じ人生を何度も生きているんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　この先の何処かでまた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,同じように廻陋に出くわす
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気付かずにまたその中を潜ってしまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また時間は繰り返し　同じ人生を味わう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,既視感を持つ者の記録はあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,全てを調べることなど到底できない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつの人生の全てを知るなんてことは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:38.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,同じことを…俺は繰り返し…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何一つ言い切ることはできんが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:48.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一応　花の匂いのする暗がりには用心したほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,廻陋に囚われた者が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,思うように過去を変えたという話は聞かない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:01.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それに　既視感を持ったということは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今までのように昔に戻ることはできないかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:12.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何度も潜るうちに　廻陋と同化してしまうかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:18.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,決して　もう一度潜ろうなどとは考えるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,変えたい過去もあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それより俺はこの先が見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:38.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,娘の成長や孫の姿や　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:43.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだ見たことのない毎日がな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おーい　郁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山菜取りに行ってくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう　気をつけてね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すっかり遅くなっちまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く帰らねぇと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:44.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺は何度もこの穴を潜った後　あの頃に戻って
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:14.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,カオル　遅かったじゃない　何かあったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:19.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　このお前は初めて見る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:27.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと幸せな悪夢を見ていたようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:31.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何よそれ　どうしたの　一体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:39.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これからはずっと新しい毎日がやって来るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　郁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:12.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　どこだ　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,郁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:22.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辛抱しろ　すぐ医者に連れてってやるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:27.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,体は冷たくなってく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ　里に着く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,決して　もう一度潜ろうなどとは考えるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なあ　郁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:11.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この中から花の匂いがする
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,里への近道かもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:21.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ　お前は助かるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:31.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そしてまた　遠い未来に　俺と一緒に暮らすんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:24.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　今　何か思い出しそうな気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:28.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,郁　どうかしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:32.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ううん　何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:36.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体何だったかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:45.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何か懐かしいような　恐ろしいような
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どちらさんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:55.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,旅の者だが　この雨で難儀している
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:58.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一晩軒を借りられんだろうか
